improved_metadata.title: Let It Foam: The Spray Foam Insulation Anthem
improved_metadata.description: This song is a parody promoting spray foam insulation, sung in the style of "Let It Go." It highlights the benefits of spray foam for energy saving and home comfort.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Let it fall, let it fall That's what insulation's for
